<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>C<ex>huncz</ex></expan>
<expan>Ödemberg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> und ein <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan>
                        knechts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und geleyts zu uns begert, ewch
                            <expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und wenn ir
                                <expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan><app>
<note><q type="date">sand Margreten tag schierist</q>13.07.1420</note>
</app>
<add>zu uns</add>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> meynt zu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so
                        süllt ir zu uns von uns, für uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<add>on geverd</add> und bey uns, für
                                <expan>all<ex>er</ex>meniklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> drey tag geleyt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewr red gern hören. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Pauli.</ab>
